          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Student Debt Repayment Fairness Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Truth in Lending Act to prohibit a private educational lender&nbsp;from accelerating the repayment terms of a borrower's outstanding loan obligation upon the death or permanent, total disability of a cosigner if the borrower is in good standing.</p>]]></text>
